Subject: [PATCH 3/5] Phase 3: Add GMCM integration with category toggles and
 localization support

- Expanded GenericModConfigMenuIntegration.cs with titleScreenOnly registration
- Added 8 category boolean options to GMCM menu
- Added progression restriction master toggle option
- Extended Reset() method to handle new config properties
- Added 21 translation keys to i18n/default.json
- Added 21 translation constant keys and getter methods to I18n.cs
- Updated Project_Development.md with Entry 7

Implements anti-temptation feature: config changes only at title screen
